Xbox Controller Button Map


Robot Control
Right Trigger:   foward movement
Left Trigger:    backWard movement
left joystick:   left/right turning
left d-pad:      left 90 degree turn(counterclockwise)
right d-pad:     right 90 degree turn(clockwise)
Y:               play theme song

Servo Control
X:               center servo position
down d-pad:      low servo position
up d-pad:        high servo position
right bumper:    increment servo position up
left bumper:     increment servo position down

